::Primal Prime::

    He walks up to Hot Rod and Firearm hearing Firearm asking about him being 
Hot Rod.
    "They are surprised to be in the presance of a legend, it may not seem 
right to people like you and me, but to them it is very cool," Primal said. 
"Wait, did I just call myself a legend?"
